File = open('Airport.txt', 'rb')
G = nx.read_weighted_edgelist(File)
nx.draw(G, with_labels=True, node_color='b')
plt.show()

print("Order of the graph is: ", G.order())
print("Size of the graph is: ", G.size())

Order of the graph is:  500
Size of the graph is:  2980
In [3]:
lines_per_file = 10
smallfile = None
with open('Airport.txt') as bigfile:
    for lineno, line in enumerate(bigfile):
        if lineno % lines_per_file == 0:
            if smallfile:
                smallfile.close()
            small_filename = 'Airport_{}.txt'.format(lineno + lines_per_file)
            smallfile = open(small_filename, "w")
        smallfile.write(line)
    if smallfile:
        smallfile.close()
